
# Project 08 — Topic Modeling (Unsupervised NLP)

This project implements an unsupervised Natural Language Processing (NLP) system to automatically discover hidden topics from a collection of text documents using TF-IDF and Non-negative Matrix Factorization (NMF).

The system groups documents based on word patterns without using any labeled data.

---

## 📌 Project Objectives

This project aims to:

- Clean and preprocess raw text data
- Convert text into numerical vectors using TF-IDF
- Learn latent topics using NMF or LDA
- Extract important words for each topic
- Document discovered topics in a readable format
- Save trained models for reuse
- Generate topic reports for analysis

